</p><p class="- topic/p ">Ambient climate conditions of the device. Three different graphs are displayed: 
</p><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Ambient Temperature 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Ambient Humidity 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Condensation temperature margin. 
